<div>
<p xml:id="subtitle1" begin="14180832t" end="34200832t" region="region0" style="style0">[주제곡]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle2" begin="221471249t" end="235234999t" region="region0" style="style0">[천둥이 우르릉 울린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle3" begin="239822916t" end="258174582t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle4" begin="264847916t" end="289872916t" region="region0" style="style0">[천둥이 우르릉 울린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle5" begin="344510832t" end="357440416t" region="region0" style="style0">[천둥이 우르릉 울린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle6" begin="371204166t" end="380797082t" region="region0" style="style0">[오싹한 효과음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle7" begin="468384582t" end="482148332t" region="region0" style="style0">(봉구)<br/>일어날 시간이야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle8" begin="491741249t" end="500917082t" region="region0" style="style0">(상우)<br/>하나</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle9" begin="507173332t" end="515514999t" region="region0" style="style0">둘</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle10" begin="531364166t" end="540540000t" region="region0" style="style0">셋<br/>[카메라 셔터음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle11" begin="541374166t" end="553469582t" region="region0" style="style0">[예림의 짜증 섞인 신음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle12" begin="555972082t" end="566399166t" region="region0" style="style0">[잔잔한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle13" begin="567233332t" end="584750832t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>[짜증 내며]<br/>야, 서상우</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle14" begin="585585000t" end="597680416t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우의 깔깔대는 웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle15" begin="602268332t" end="628544582t" region="region0" style="style0">야, 너 어제 라면 먹고 잤지?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle16" begin="630212916t" end="645645000t" region="region0" style="style0">얼굴 완전 빵빵해<br/>[상우가 크게 웃는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle17" begin="646479166t" end="666499166t" region="region0" style="style0">아, 뭐야, 좋은 말로 할 때<br/>그거 안 지워?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle18" begin="667333332t" end="681931250t" region="region0" style="style0">- (상우) 에헤<br/>- (예림) 아이씨</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle19" begin="683182500t" end="706122082t" region="region0" style="style0">(상우)<br/>그래도 내가 잠만 주무시는<br/>게으른 반장님 대신에</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle20" begin="706956250t" end="729895832t" region="region0" style="style0">제가 전달 사항을 받아 왔다고요</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle21" begin="741157082t" end="755755000t" region="region0" style="style0">오늘 조회 없고 자습하래</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle22" begin="764096666t" end="778277500t" region="region0" style="style0">무슨 소리야?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle23" begin="779111666t" end="800800000t" region="region0" style="style0">[웃으며]<br/>아니, 우리 고귀하신<br/>담임 선생님께서</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle24" begin="801634166t" end="814980832t" region="region0" style="style0">어제부로 입원하셨대</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle25" begin="815815000t" end="834166666t" region="region0" style="style0">뭐, 계단에서 미끄러졌다나 뭐라나</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle26" begin="840422916t" end="849181666t" region="region0" style="style0">허리가</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle27" begin="861694166t" end="870035832t" region="region0" style="style0">똑</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle28" begin="879628749t" end="888387499t" region="region0" style="style0">정말?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle29" begin="893392499t" end="914663749t" region="region0" style="style0">아이, 자고로 남자의 생명은<br/>허리인데</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle30" begin="920502916t" end="935517916t" region="region0" style="style0">뭐, 수술 어쩌고<br/>하는 거 들으니까</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle31" begin="936352082t" end="951784166t" region="region0" style="style0">뭐, 당분간 컴백은 힘들걸?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle32" begin="958874582t" end="979311666t" region="region0" style="style0">아이, 어떡해, 우리 쌤</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle33" begin="990989999t" end="1000582916t" region="region0" style="style0">어머</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle34" begin="1008090416t" end="1017266249t" region="region0" style="style0">예림아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle35" begin="1029778749t" end="1048547499t" region="region0" style="style0">넌 어쩌면 이렇게<br/>마음씨까지 고와?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle36" begin="1055220832t" end="1081497082t" region="region0" style="style0">그렇게 맨날 부려 먹는<br/>나쁜 담임 걱정도 다 해 주고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle37" begin="1082331250t" end="1091924166t" region="region0" style="style0">[예림의 멋쩍은 웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle38" begin="1092758332t" end="1103185416t" region="region0" style="style0">[이를 악물며]<br/>그만해라</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle39" begin="1119034582t" end="1133215416t" region="region0" style="style0">씁<br/>[멋쩍은 웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle40" begin="1134049582t" end="1143642500t" region="region0" style="style0">그런데 있잖아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle41" begin="1145310832t" end="1154486666t" region="region0" style="style0">짬 나면</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle42" begin="1176175000t" end="1203702500t" region="region0" style="style0">이제 이 서방님 걱정도<br/>좀 해 주면 안 될까?<br/>[예림의 기가 찬 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle43" begin="1204536666t" end="1231647082t" region="region0" style="style0">나는 맨날 우리 마누라 생각으로<br/>가득 차 있는데</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle44" begin="1242491250t" end="1252918332t" region="region0" style="style0">응<br/>[장난스러운 웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle45" begin="1254586666t" end="1262928332t" region="region0" style="style0">그러게<br/>[상우의 옅은 신음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle46" begin="1263762500t" end="1274606666t" region="region0" style="style0">야, 서방은 무슨</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle47" begin="1276692082t" end="1285867916t" region="region0" style="style0">매번 이야기해 주는데</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle48" begin="1286702082t" end="1297963332t" region="region0" style="style0">학습 효과가 없네<br/>[상우의 옅은 신음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle49" begin="1298797500t" end="1307139166t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우가 살짝 웃는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle50" begin="1307973332t" end="1322571250t" region="region0" style="style0">- 내 놔, 카메라<br/>- 어, 야, 이건 안 되지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle51" begin="1323405416t" end="1335083750t" region="region0" style="style0">- 내 놔<br/>- 이건 안 되지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle52" begin="1335917916t" end="1344676666t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>내 놔</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle53" begin="1345510832t" end="1357606250t" region="region0" style="style0">- 이럴 줄 알았지<br/>- 이거 진짜 지워라</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle54" begin="1358440416t" end="1370535832t" region="region0" style="style0">(상우)<br/>이럴 줄 알았지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle55" begin="1371370000t" end="1401817082t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]<br/>[상우와 예림이 실랑이를 벌인다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle56" begin="1434766666t" end="1451032916t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>교실에 갇힌 아이들은</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle57" begin="1463545416t" end="1480645832t" region="region0" style="style0">가끔 엉뚱한 상상을 한다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle58" begin="1513178332t" end="1530278750t" region="region0" style="style0">전쟁이 일어나면 어떨까?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle59" begin="1548630416t" end="1572404166t" region="region0" style="style0">지진이 나서<br/>학교가 무너져 버리는 것도</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle60" begin="1574072500t" end="1583248332t" region="region0" style="style0">괜찮겠지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle61" begin="1628293332t" end="1648313332t" region="region0" style="style0">나에게 세상을 바꿀 힘이 있다면</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle62" begin="1665413750t" end="1680011666t" region="region0" style="style0">세상은 좋아질까?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle63" begin="1700031666t" end="1711292916t" region="region0" style="style0">내가 꾸는 꿈은</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle64" begin="1731312916t" end="1747579166t" region="region0" style="style0">언젠가 이루어지긴 할까?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle65" begin="1776357916t" end="1798880416t" region="region0" style="style0">진심으로 간절하게 소망한다면</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle66" begin="1841839999t" end="1853101249t" region="region0" style="style0">이루어질까?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle67" begin="1862277082t" end="1883131249t" region="region0" style="style0">[분위기가 고조되는 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle68" begin="1903985416t" end="1913578332t" region="region0" style="style0">(은아)<br/>야, 야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle69" begin="1921502916t" end="1951949999t" region="region0" style="style0">우리 학교에<br/>투명 인간이 살고 있다는 얘기</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle70" begin="1954452499t" end="1966130832t" region="region0" style="style0">들어 봤어?<br/>[별의 놀라는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle71" begin="1966964999t" end="1976140832t" region="region0" style="style0">(별)<br/>진짜?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle72" begin="1986567916t" end="1998246249t" region="region0" style="style0">학교에만 오면</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle73" begin="2003251249t" end="2019934582t" region="region0" style="style0">다른 애들 눈에 보이지 않는</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle74" begin="2020768749t" end="2036617916t" region="region0" style="style0">투명 인간으로 변한대</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle75" begin="2038703332t" end="2066230832t" region="region0" style="style0">[별의 두려운 숨소리]<br/>야, 개무섭다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle76" begin="2076240832t" end="2085416666t" region="region0" style="style0">아니</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle77" begin="2090421666t" end="2109190416t" region="region0" style="style0">그런데 걔 혹시</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle78" begin="2120868749t" end="2135883749t" region="region0" style="style0">우리 반에 있는 거 아니야?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle79" begin="2142557082t" end="2152150000t" region="region0" style="style0">[은아의 멋쩍은 웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle80" begin="2155903750t" end="2171752916t" region="region0" style="style0">설마 아니겠지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle81" begin="2190521666t" end="2212627082t" region="region0" style="style0">우리 반에 그런<br/>투명 인간이 있다니</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle82" begin="2218466250t" end="2230561666t" region="region0" style="style0">말이 되니?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle83" begin="2233481250t" end="2248913332t" region="region0" style="style0">아, 완전 소름 끼친다<br/>[은아의 웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle84" begin="2249747500t" end="2259340416t" region="region0" style="style0">[물병을 툭 친다]<br/>(별)<br/>어?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle85" begin="2273104166t" end="2293124166t" region="region0" style="style0">[별의 어색한 웃음]<br/>[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle86" begin="2303551250t" end="2311892916t" region="region0" style="style0">‘소리’</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle87" begin="2333998332t" end="2342340000t" region="region0" style="style0">(은아)<br/>왜?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle88" begin="2352767082t" end="2366947916t" region="region0" style="style0">무슨 일 있었어?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle89" begin="2374455416t" end="2387802082t" region="region0" style="style0">난 잘 모르겠는데</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle90" begin="2394475416t" end="2413244166t" region="region0" style="style0">[함께 깔깔 웃는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle91" begin="2417832082t" end="2426173750t" region="region0" style="style0">[손뼉을 짝 맞춘다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle92" begin="2429510416t" end="2439103332t" region="region0" style="style0">[별이 살짝 웃는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle93" begin="2452450000t" end="2467882082t" region="region0" style="style0">[학교 종소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle94" begin="2468716250t" end="2480394582t" region="region0" style="style0">(병진과 지석)<br/>가위, 바위, 보</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle95" begin="2481228750t" end="2493324166t" region="region0" style="style0">[병진의 기합]<br/>[지석의 아파하는 신음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle96" begin="2494992500t" end="2509590416t" region="region0" style="style0">[친구들의 웃음]<br/>(지석)<br/>야, 씨, 한 번 더 해</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle97" begin="2522102916t" end="2542122916t" region="region0" style="style0">[신비로운 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle98" begin="2634298332t" end="2650981666t" region="region0" style="style0">(병진)<br/>야, 알았어, 알았어<br/>알았어, 알았어</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle99" begin="2651815832t" end="2667247916t" region="region0" style="style0">- (병진) 미안해, 미안해<br/>- 도망가? 이 새끼야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle100" begin="2668082082t" end="2692272916t" region="region0" style="style0">- 야, 미안, 진짜 미안하다<br/>- 도망가? 이게 죽으려고<br/>[칠판을 똑똑 두드린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle101" begin="2695609582t" end="2717297916t" region="region0" style="style0">(병진)<br/>아, 아프다니까, 진짜</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle102" begin="2843257082t" end="2854935416t" region="region0" style="style0">[의자를 쓱 민다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle103" begin="2859523332t" end="2868699166t" region="region0" style="style0">차렷</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle104" begin="2872035832t" end="2880794582t" region="region0" style="style0">응</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle105" begin="2919583332t" end="2928342082t" region="region0" style="style0">오늘부로</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle106" begin="2946693750t" end="2967965000t" region="region0" style="style0">[분필로 글씨를 쓴다]<br/>2학년 3반</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle107" begin="2977140832t" end="2990904582t" region="region0" style="style0">임시 담임을 맡은</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle108" begin="3058055000t" end="3067230832t" region="region0" style="style0">한봉구다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle109" begin="3108522082t" end="3134381250t" region="region0" style="style0">언제까지 임시 담임을<br/>하게 될지는 잘 모르겠지만</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle110" begin="3145225416t" end="3158155000t" region="region0" style="style0">2학년 3반</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle111" begin="3161491666t" end="3178592082t" region="region0" style="style0">너희들에 대해 더 많이 알고 싶고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle112" begin="3181928750t" end="3198612082t" region="region0" style="style0">더 많은 도움이 되었으면 좋겠다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle113" begin="3209873332t" end="3219466250t" region="region0" style="style0">그런 의미에서</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle114" begin="3226973750t" end="3241571666t" region="region0" style="style0">오늘부터 한 사람씩</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle115" begin="3242405832t" end="3261591666t" region="region0" style="style0">개별 진로 상담을 시작하겠다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle116" begin="3262425832t" end="3272852916t" region="region0" style="style0">[학생들이 웅성거린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle117" begin="3274938332t" end="3291204582t" region="region0" style="style0">(재수)<br/>다음 주부터 시험 기간인데</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle118" begin="3302882916t" end="3324571250t" region="region0" style="style0">개별 상담은 나중에 해도<br/>되는 거 아닌가요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle119" begin="3342088750t" end="3351264582t" region="region0" style="style0">[봉구의 피식하는 웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle120" begin="3367113749t" end="3383379999t" region="region0" style="style0">22번 천재수</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle121" begin="3384214166t" end="3396309582t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle122" begin="3401731666t" end="3428842082t" region="region0" style="style0">만년 2등만 하는 불운의 모범생</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle123" begin="3443022916t" end="3463877082t" region="region0" style="style0">2학년 3반 부동의 1등은</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle124" begin="3494324166t" end="3505168332t" region="region0" style="style0">3번 강예림</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle125" begin="3545208332t" end="3562308749t" region="region0" style="style0">세상은 1등만 기억하지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle126" begin="3570650416t" end="3584414166t" region="region0" style="style0">2등은 기억하지 않는다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle127" begin="3621534582t" end="3639469166t" region="region0" style="style0">[작은 소리로]<br/>넌 기억되지 못하겠지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle128" begin="3695775416t" end="3714961249t" region="region0" style="style0">원치 않는 사람은 패스해도 좋다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle129" begin="3720800416t" end="3732061666t" region="region0" style="style0">하지만 장담하지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle130" begin="3739986249t" end="3754167082t" region="region0" style="style0">분명 재미있고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle131" begin="3756669582t" end="3772101666t" region="region0" style="style0">유익한 시간이 될 거라고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle132" begin="3796709582t" end="3805885416t" region="region0" style="style0">지원자?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle133" begin="3830910416t" end="3840086249t" region="region0" style="style0">(은아)<br/>저요</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle134" begin="3860523332t" end="3878874999t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle135" begin="3927673749t" end="3941020416t" region="region0" style="style0">6번 김슬기</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle136" begin="3944357082t" end="3955201249t" region="region0" style="style0">좋다<br/>[슬기의 당황한 신음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle137" begin="3959372082t" end="3972718749t" region="region0" style="style0">2시까지 상담실로 오도록</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle138" begin="3982728749t" end="3992738749t" region="region0" style="style0">[못마땅한 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle139" begin="4000246249t" end="4016512499t" region="region0" style="style0">[급식실이 소란스럽다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle140" begin="4081577499t" end="4094924166t" region="region0" style="style0">(슬기)<br/>아!<br/>[슬기의 신음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle141" begin="4104099999t" end="4122868749t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]<br/>[슬기의 떨리는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle142" begin="4165828332t" end="4175004166t" region="region0" style="style0">[슬기가 코를 훌쩍인다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle143" begin="4194189999t" end="4212124582t" region="region0" style="style0">[슬기의 울먹이는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle144" begin="4222551666t" end="4231727499t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우의 옅은 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle145" begin="4236732499t" end="4249662082t" region="region0" style="style0">싸가지없는 것들</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle146" begin="4255084166t" end="4265094166t" region="region0" style="style0">누구야, 발 건 게?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle147" begin="4274687082t" end="4286782499t" region="region0" style="style0">(은아)<br/>누구야? 도대체</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle148" begin="4289284999t" end="4301797500t" region="region0" style="style0">[상미가 살짝 웃는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle149" begin="4304300000t" end="4320983332t" region="region0" style="style0">- (은아) 너야?<br/>- (별) 아니</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle150" begin="4323485832t" end="4337666666t" region="region0" style="style0">그럼 너야?<br/>[아영의 부정하는 콧소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle151" begin="4342254582t" end="4361023332t" region="region0" style="style0">[슬기의 울먹이는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle152" begin="4399812082t" end="4409822082t" region="region0" style="style0">(은아)<br/>[웃으며]<br/>누구야?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle153" begin="4436515416t" end="4458620832t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle154" begin="4578740832t" end="4587916666t" region="region0" style="style0">[심호흡]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle155" begin="4616695416t" end="4627122500t" region="region0" style="style0">[똑똑]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle156" begin="4664242916t" end="4681760416t" region="region0" style="style0">[똑딱똑딱]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle157" begin="4700112082t" end="4715544166t" region="region0" style="style0">(봉구)<br/>투명 인간 김슬기</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle158" begin="4753915832t" end="4762674582t" region="region0" style="style0">네?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle159" begin="4765177082t" end="4787699582t" region="region0" style="style0">존재하지만 보이지 않는 투명 인간</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle160" begin="4815227082t" end="4824820000t" region="region0" style="style0">저 갈래요</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle161" begin="4827322500t" end="4836081250t" region="region0" style="style0">왜?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle162" begin="4869447916t" end="4888216666t" region="region0" style="style0">진실을 말했을 뿐인데</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle163" begin="4892387500t" end="4901980416t" region="region0" style="style0">기분 나쁜가?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle164" begin="4902814582t" end="4928673750t" region="region0" style="style0">[메트로놈이 똑딱거린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle165" begin="4937432500t" end="4954532916t" region="region0" style="style0">저에 대해 뭘 아시는데요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle166" begin="4969547916t" end="4992070416t" region="region0" style="style0">처음 오신<br/>기간제 선생님일 뿐이면서</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle167" begin="4999160832t" end="5025437082t" region="region0" style="style0">[숨을 들이마시며]<br/>5개월 전</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle168" begin="5033361666t" end="5057135416t" region="region0" style="style0">반에서 괴롭힘당하는 친구의 문제를</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle169" begin="5059637916t" end="5073401666t" region="region0" style="style0">담임한테 얘기했었지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle170" begin="5088416666t" end="5098009582t" region="region0" style="style0">왜?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle171" begin="5104265832t" end="5112607500t" region="region0" style="style0">갑자기</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle172" begin="5118029582t" end="5134712916t" region="region0" style="style0">죄책감이라도 생겼던 건가?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle173" begin="5150979166t" end="5161406250t" region="region0" style="style0">사실 너도</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle174" begin="5173084582t" end="5196024166t" region="region0" style="style0">그 친구 괴롭히는 데<br/>한몫했었으면서</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle175" begin="5223551666t" end="5233144582t" region="region0" style="style0">[슬기가 옅은 숨을 내뱉는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle176" begin="5264842916t" end="5289450832t" region="region0" style="style0">그 카밀러는 마음을 안정시켜 주지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle177" begin="5290702082t" end="5311556250t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle178" begin="5326988332t" end="5336581250t" region="region0" style="style0">[옅은 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle179" begin="5404148750t" end="5413324582t" region="region0" style="style0">[슬기가 꿀꺽 삼킨다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle180" begin="5425002916t" end="5433761666t" region="region0" style="style0">[컵을 탁 놓는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle181" begin="5445022916t" end="5454615832t" region="region0" style="style0">[옅은 숨을 내뱉는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle182" begin="5486314166t" end="5511339166t" region="region0" style="style0">너무하다 싶었어요</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle183" begin="5519680832t" end="5545540000t" region="region0" style="style0">왕따를 당하던 친구는<br/>전학을 가 버렸고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle184" begin="5550545000t" end="5579323750t" region="region0" style="style0">괴롭히던 아이들은<br/>아무런 처벌도 받지 않았지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle185" begin="5583911666t" end="5593504582t" region="region0" style="style0">달라진 건</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle186" begin="5606434166t" end="5623117500t" region="region0" style="style0">그때부터 김슬기 네가</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle187" begin="5632710416t" end="5650645000t" region="region0" style="style0">타깃으로 변경됐을 뿐</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle188" begin="5669830832t" end="5691936250t" region="region0" style="style0">담임 쌤이<br/>그렇게 말씀해 주셨어요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle189" begin="5693604582t" end="5708202500t" region="region0" style="style0">그게 그렇게 중요한가?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle190" begin="5727805416t" end="5743654582t" region="region0" style="style0">담임은 널 방관했어</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle191" begin="5750745000t" end="5762423332t" region="region0" style="style0">선생이란 게</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle192" begin="5765342916t" end="5789533750t" region="region0" style="style0">다들 자기 밥그릇<br/>챙기기 바쁜 놈들이니까</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle193" begin="5814558750t" end="5823734582t" region="region0" style="style0">[슬기의 옅은 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle194" begin="5834995832t" end="5847091250t" region="region0" style="style0">되돌리고 싶지 않아?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle195" begin="5857518332t" end="5866277082t" region="region0" style="style0">이 모든 걸?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle196" begin="5922166250t" end="5932593332t" region="region0" style="style0">어떻게요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle197" begin="5948442500t" end="5957618332t" region="region0" style="style0">[숨을 살짝 들이켠다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle198" begin="5958452500t" end="5978055416t" region="region0" style="style0">이제부터 네가 들어야 될 얘기야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle199" begin="6028105416t" end="6040617916t" region="region0" style="style0">[봉구의 옅은 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle200" begin="6088999582t" end="6111105000t" region="region0" style="style0">여기에 네가 원하는 관계도를<br/>만들어 봐</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle201" begin="6126537082t" end="6149476666t" region="region0" style="style0">만들어 보라고요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle202" begin="6212873332t" end="6239983750t" region="region0" style="style0">[종이를 사락 펼친다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle203" begin="6251245000t" end="6274184582t" region="region0" style="style0">[불길한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle204" begin="6435595832t" end="6444771666t" region="region0" style="style0">[불길함이 고조되는 효과음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle205" begin="6445605832t" end="6454364582t" region="region0" style="style0">(별)<br/>슬기야!</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle206" begin="6455198750t" end="6463957500t" region="region0" style="style0">[별의 달려오는 발걸음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle207" begin="6474801666t" end="6490650832t" region="region0" style="style0">야, 너 영어 숙제했어?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle208" begin="6520680832t" end="6536530000t" region="region0" style="style0">하긴 했는데</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle209" begin="6538198332t" end="6548625416t" region="region0" style="style0">어휴, 살았다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle210" begin="6553630416t" end="6589916666t" region="region0" style="style0">아니, 나 이 부분이<br/>해석이 완전 안 되는 거야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle211" begin="6590750832t" end="6600760832t" region="region0" style="style0">그래서 그러는데</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle212" begin="6605348750t" end="6632042082t" region="region0" style="style0">나 여기만 살짝<br/>베끼면 안 될까, 응?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle213" begin="6632876250t" end="6653730416t" region="region0" style="style0">슬기야, 너 영어 잘하잖아, 응?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle214" begin="6656650000t" end="6674584582t" region="region0" style="style0">한 번만 슬기야, 어?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle215" begin="6675418750t" end="6688348332t" region="region0" style="style0">- 자, 잠시만...<br/>- 어</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle216" begin="6692519166t" end="6710036666t" region="region0" style="style0">(아영)<br/>야, 너희 어제 뮤뱅 봤음?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle217" begin="6710870832t" end="6720046666t" region="region0" style="style0">(별)<br/>아니, 왜?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle218" begin="6720880832t" end="6751327916t" region="region0" style="style0">[숨을 내뱉으며]<br/>대박, 박빙 어제 컴백했잖아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle219" begin="6752996249t" end="6765508749t" region="region0" style="style0">- (별) 진짜?<br/>- (아영) 그래</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle220" begin="6766342916t" end="6788031249t" region="region0" style="style0">- (별) 아, 놓쳤다, 아<br/>- 슬기, 너도 못 봤어?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle221" begin="6808051249t" end="6830990832t" region="region0" style="style0">[무거운 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle222" begin="6844337499t" end="6855598749t" region="region0" style="style0">[울먹이는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle223" begin="6861437916t" end="6869779582t" region="region0" style="style0">[코를 훌쩍인다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle224" begin="6872699166t" end="6906899999t" region="region0" style="style0">[흐느낀다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle225" begin="6941934999t" end="6964040416t" region="region0" style="style0">(아영)<br/>야, 갑자기 왜 그래?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle226" begin="6970296666t" end="6981140832t" region="region0" style="style0">[슬기가 흐느낀다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle227" begin="6990733749t" end="7001160832t" region="region0" style="style0">[울음 섞인 웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle228" begin="7005748749t" end="7019512499t" region="region0" style="style0">아니<br/>[코를 훌쩍인다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle229" begin="7020763749t" end="7048291249t" region="region0" style="style0">그냥 꿈꾸고 있나 해서</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle230" begin="7053713332t" end="7064140416t" region="region0" style="style0">[별의 멋쩍은 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle231" begin="7067894166t" end="7092084999t" region="region0" style="style0">(별)<br/>얘가 벌써부터 고3 스트레스인가?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle232" begin="7103763332t" end="7129622499t" region="region0" style="style0">야, 김슬기, 너 오버야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle233" begin="7133376249t" end="7145888749t" region="region0" style="style0">울지 마, 뚝</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle234" begin="7155481666t" end="7164657499t" region="region0" style="style0">(별)<br/>야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle235" begin="7168411249t" end="7177587082t" region="region0" style="style0">[별의 웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle236" begin="7186345832t" end="7196772916t" region="region0" style="style0">(은아)<br/>너희들 뭐해?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle237" begin="7220129582t" end="7232642082t" region="region0" style="style0">야, 대박</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle238" begin="7235144582t" end="7254747499t" region="region0" style="style0">슬기 얘기하다가 갑자기 막 운다?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle239" begin="7255581666t" end="7267677082t" region="region0" style="style0">내 말은 그게 아니잖아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle240" begin="7285611666t" end="7301043749t" region="region0" style="style0">왜 투명 인간하고 말 섞고 있냐고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle241" begin="7306465832t" end="7318144166t" region="region0" style="style0">고은아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle242" begin="7323983332t" end="7338581249t" region="region0" style="style0">그만하면 됐잖아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle243" begin="7341500832t" end="7349842499t" region="region0" style="style0">뭐?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle244" begin="7368611249t" end="7377787082t" region="region0" style="style0">너희들</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle245" begin="7385294582t" end="7400309582t" region="region0" style="style0">얘가 어떤 애인지 잊은 거야?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle246" begin="7403229166t" end="7417827082t" region="region0" style="style0">(아영)<br/>우리도 잘한 거 없잖아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle247" begin="7421997916t" end="7437847082t" region="region0" style="style0">이제 그만 좀 하지?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle248" begin="7441600832t" end="7452027916t" region="region0" style="style0">[은아의 기가 찬 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle249" begin="7472464999t" end="7492484999t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle250" begin="7505831666t" end="7525017499t" region="region0" style="style0">애들이 좀 받아 주니까 좋냐?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle251" begin="7543786249t" end="7554630416t" region="region0" style="style0">근데 어쩌냐</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle252" begin="7573399166t" end="7588831249t" region="region0" style="style0">배신자는 배신자인데</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle253" begin="7597589999t" end="7605931666t" region="region0" style="style0">(별)<br/>야, 은아야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle254" begin="7629288332t" end="7638047082t" region="region0" style="style0">[문을 똑똑 두드린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle255" begin="7752327916t" end="7761503749t" region="region0" style="style0">저기...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle256" begin="7763172082t" end="7781523749t" region="region0" style="style0">상황판하고 펜은 두고 가도록</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle257" begin="7816975832t" end="7849925416t" region="region0" style="style0">이거 좀 더 쓸 수 있을까요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle258" begin="7853679166t" end="7879121249t" region="region0" style="style0">어제부로 친한 친구가<br/>두 명이나 생겼을 텐데</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle259" begin="7885794582t" end="7899141249t" region="region0" style="style0">그걸로는 만족이 안 돼?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle260" begin="7907482916t" end="7925834582t" region="region0" style="style0">[멋쩍게 웃으며]<br/>네, 그게...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle261" begin="7932924999t" end="7959201249t" region="region0" style="style0">뭐, 안 될 건 없지만</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle262" begin="7973799166t" end="7996738749t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle263" begin="8010919582t" end="8025100416t" region="region0" style="style0">[메트로놈 소리가 울린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle264" begin="8182757916t" end="8201526666t" region="region0" style="style0">(슬기)<br/>계약 같은 건가요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle265" begin="8277018749t" end="8287445832t" region="region0" style="style0">할게요</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle266" begin="8330822499t" end="8342500832t" region="region0" style="style0">[날카로운 효과음]<br/>[아파하는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle267" begin="8400892499t" end="8410068332t" region="region0" style="style0">계약</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle268" begin="8415907499t" end="8425500416t" region="region0" style="style0">성립</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle269" begin="8443017916t" end="8453027916t" region="region0" style="style0">[똑딱]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle270" begin="8463037916t" end="8480138332t" region="region0" style="style0">[기괴한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle271" begin="8489314166t" end="8499741249t" region="region0" style="style0">[쿵 하는 효과음]</p>
